PQueue version 0.21
===================

PQueue is nothing more than a simple perl module to interface with Tunez, a
GPL'ed music jukebox which features MP3, OGG support with multiuser voting.

PQueue allows a consistent perl interface to controlling playback which allows
the user to use the provided perl interfaces or write their own to customize
playback.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

DBD
DBD::Mysql
Tunez v1.21

